longBusinessSummary: Inter-Rock Minerals Inc., through its subsidiaires, produces and distributes specialty feed ingredients in the United States and Canada. It also produces and markets dolomite for the animal feed, glass, roofing, and aglime industries. The company is based in Toronto, Canada.
